       Rampage, Tankkor, Inferno, Marine, and Gremlin went to the outside of 
the ship. There were numerous repair drones re-enforcing the hull and 
repairing overloaded autoguns. The foursome climed to the top of the vessle, 
and took positions on four powerful manule attack canons. They were double 
barrled plasma and particle guns with a semicircular covering in front, but 
behinde the shields there was no risk of being hit.
       The four Predacons targeted Galvatron, Destructor, Darkfate, and the 
other Destrons. The blasts sent a loud and powerful crack of discharge flying 
at the bots.

--part1_b5.78f41f5.27cad73f_boundary
